Từ điển Anh - Việt
◘[iks'tensivli]
*phó từ
 ■rộng rãi, bao quát, cùng khắp
 ⁃they travelled extensively in Southeast Asia
 hòtưng đi nhiều nơi ở Đông Nam á

sentences.en: They travelled extensively in Southeast Asia.
sentences.vi: Họ từng đi nhiều nơi ở Đông Nam á.

sentences.en: He has also written extensively on contemporary English usage.

sentences.en: These are known as nuclides and are used extensively in radiotherapy for the treatment of cancer.

sentences.en: He worked extensively in his home area, quickly gaining a reputation as a hot player.

sentences.en: You will see this swapping technique used extensively throughout the sort methods presented in this chapter.
